Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.98,0:00:06.98,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\fnSapirSans\c&H9FA2A6&\3c&H201E23&\move(404,391,377,391,0,3985)}Yagami
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki has asked for your help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, Ryuuzaki has asked for your help with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing to help, we need you to come here as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.01,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was thinking of how to start discussing the subject with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that they would approach me with this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this manner, I'll be able to investigate both the Investigative Headquarters and the fake Kira as much as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it takes, I've got to find the fake Kira before they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yagami-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem; {\alpha&HFF&}after all, we both want to catch Kira, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem; after all, we both want to catch Kira, Ryuuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me "Ryuuzaki" while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.72,0:00:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm Asahi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, does that make me "Asahi Light"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, That is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're here, I'll call you "Light-kun".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.61,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for throwing you in at the deep end, but I need you to look over all the current material we have on the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,including the videos that were sent to the Japanese TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I can't let you take any of the material away, or make notes of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:23.72,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(357,391)}Last night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... {\alpha&HFF&}we'll proceed by hiding the possibility of a second Kira, and by having Yagami Light assist us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.23,0:01:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... we'll proceed by hiding the possibility of a second Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and by having Yagami Light assist us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... we'll proceed by hiding the possibility of a second Kira, and by having Yagami Light assist us with the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-{\alpha&HFF&}But won't it be hard for us to investigate with him if we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But won't it be hard for us to investigate with him if we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. {\alpha&HFF&}What's the point in him helping us in this investigation anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. What's the point in him helping us in this investigation anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we only need to hide this from him till we've heard his opinions on these videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun's skills of deduction are truly quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees these videos, {\alpha&HFF&}he may be able to deduce that this is the work of a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he sees these videos, he may be able to deduce that this is the work of a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be a second Kira since the victims were ones Kira normally wouldn't have killed, "since they only committed minor crimes",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's the only basis you have, isn't it Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, we've assumed that Kira needs a face and a name in order to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.61,0:02:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, from the fact that Ukita-san was killed when he happened to rush to the TV station that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from the fact that Kira spoke as if they could kill L merely by having him appear on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can come to the conclusion that the second Kira can kill people merely by seeing their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If, after reviewing the case and watching these videos,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.64,0:02:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is able to deduce that there is a second Kira, the majority of my suspicions against him will be lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Ryuuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's evident that Kira wants to kill the L who has been leading the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things continue to progress as they are, I will die after appearing on TV in three days' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that Kira would let an opportunity like this pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if my son doesn't manage to deduce that there is a second Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean that your suspicions will deepen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}If that happens, my suspicions will remain at 5% or lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. If that happens, my suspicions will remain at 5% or lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll reveal to him that we're investigating the possibility of a second Kira, and have him assist us with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:24.68,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I believe that you have understood from this that I am Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.95,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}On the date and time specified...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching these videos... {\alpha&HFF&}the terrible quality of them makes me feel sick... is that just because I am the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching these videos... the terrible quality of them makes me feel sick... {\alpha&HFF&}is that just because I am the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching these videos... the terrible quality of them makes me feel sick... is that just because I am the real Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far more serious than a simple drop in my image as Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why has no one offered any explanations for any of these videos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something odd going on here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I better not say anything stupid regarding this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave things as they are, L will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going, Light-kun? {\alpha&HFF&}Have you been able to deduce anything from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it going, Light-kun? Have you been able to deduce anything from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility that there's more than one person who has Kira's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-{\alpha&HFF&}Kira's power? What are you saying, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kira's power? {\alpha&HFF&}What are you saying, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kira's power? What are you saying, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, {\alpha&HFF&}there's a high probability that this is not the same Kira that we've been dealing with until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, there's a high probability that this is not the same Kira that we've been dealing with until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira we've been dealing with until now would not have utilized the suspects used in this broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the fact that if Kira does indeed need a name and a face to kill, {\alpha&HFF&}it's strange that they were able to kill the policemen who merely happened to go to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Add the fact that if Kira does indeed need a name and a face to kill, it's strange that they were able to kill the policemen who merely happened to go to the TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-{\alpha&HFF&}It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as L... {\alpha&HFF&}I mean, that's exactly the same theory as Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as L... I mean, that's exactly the same theory as Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-{\alpha&HFF&}Well done, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well done, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspicions against you should now be lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light-kun. {\alpha&HFF&}We also believe that there's a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light-kun. We also believe that there's a second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew, Ryuuga? {\alpha&HFF&}I mean.. Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already knew, Ryuuga? I mean.. Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were testing me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't testing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:05:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the only one to have come up with the "second Kira" theory, people may have trouble believing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've come to the same conclusion as I did, it's become a much more convincing viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, you really are extremely helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, we have to stop the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evidently, they sympathize with Kira, but they aren't very intelligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might even obey the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, {\alpha&HFF&}there's a good chance that we might be able to stop them by sending them a message from the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, there's a good chance that we might be able to stop them by sending them a message from the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have expected nothing less from you, Ryuuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also thinking of that as the best course of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you, Light-kun, {\alpha&HFF&}to play the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you, Light-kun, to play the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\alpha&HFF&}With your talent, it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. With your talent, it shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, we don't have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you write a response from "Kira" ready to be aired on this evening's news?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you planned all along? Is that why you brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think I became Kira, just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very good... but unless you take out the bit that says, "I don't mind if you kill L"... I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. If I were in Kira's shoes, in the current situation, I'm sure I'd order L's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a joke. {\alpha&HFF&}You can change it to whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a joke. You can change it to whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aihara-san, {\alpha&HFF&}the report is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aihara-san, the report is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A terrible thing has occurred!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In response to the videos sent in by Kira and aired on Sakura TV, messages have been received from another person claiming that they are the real Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have demanded that the message from the real Kira is broadcast on all TV channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Police Headquarters have agreed for the video to be broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kira? {\alpha&HFF&}Or are they both Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Kira? Or are they both Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, take a look at this video sent in by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.40,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I got a response from Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:14.29,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the real Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}and those videos sent to Sakura TV were not from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:19.62,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the real Kira, and those videos sent to Sakura TV were not from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:23.23,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, I will tolerate the actions of the one that is taking my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:29.13,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,They have worked on my behalf, and have tried to aid me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:30.89,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}taking the lives of innocent people is directly against my beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:35.55,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,However, taking the lives of innocent people is directly against my beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:41.98,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person taking my name holds the same beliefs as I, and is willing to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:47.36,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,they must stop acting impulsively, and learn to understand my true intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:50.82,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not heed this warning, you will leave me with no choice but to pass judgement on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see now... Video, video!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I'm gonna send a response to Kira right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.87,MINOR SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,390)}A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! {\alpha&HFF&}We've received a response from the second Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki! We've received a response from the second Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the envelope and everything else over as soon as I can; {\alpha&HFF&}for the moment, I'm sending a copy to your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring the envelope and everything else over as soon as I can; for the moment, I'm sending a copy to your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.98,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira-san, {\alpha&HFF&}thank you for your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.26,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira-san, thank you for your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.47,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do as you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will do as you ask", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell whether I can use them or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they truly understood Kira's feelings, {\alpha&HFF&}they should have enforced L's appearance on TV, and killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they truly understood Kira's feelings, they should have enforced L's appearance on TV, and killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess things up... {\alpha&HFF&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess things up... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.91,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet you, Kira-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:45.71,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that you have the eyes, but don't worry, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this idiot thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about the Shinigami's eyes on a video that's being broadcast to the entire nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't believe that you have the eyes"? What is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:09:02.18,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Please think of a way that we can meet without the police finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.21,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we meet, {\alpha&HFF&}we can confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:07.77,KiraVideo,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we meet, we can confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is hopeless... {\alpha&HFF&}If I don't do something fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This person is hopeless... If I don't do something fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryuuzaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ryuuzaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-{\alpha&HFF&}Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me... {\alpha&HFF&}that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me... that such things exist?!
Comment: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me.. {\alpha&HFF&}that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to tell me.. that such things exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that they exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Ryuuzaki. {\alpha&HFF&}There's no way that Shinigami actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Ryuuzaki. There's no way that Shinigami actually exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira used prisoners to write sentences about Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, {\alpha&HFF&}shouldn't we consider this to be the work of the original Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true, shouldn't we consider this to be the work of the original Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same words from the same person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira we have dealt with until now wouldn't have replied to our video.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira wouldn't have bought this story. And they wouldn't have prevented L from going on TV to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, {\alpha&HFF&}is there a possibility that the real Kira and the second Kira may already have joined forces, and are using the term "Shinigami" to confuse our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is there a possibility that the real Kira and the second Kira may already have joined forces, {\alpha&HFF&}and are using the term "Shinigami" to confuse our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is there a possibility that the real Kira and the second Kira may already have joined forces, and are using the term "Shinigami" to confuse our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there's any chance of that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun is correct. If Kira is involved, I doubt that they'd stop trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This second Kira appears to be acting on their own interests, rather than Kira's beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, {\alpha&HFF&}their desire to meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, their desire to meet Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are acting on their own curiosity about Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps "Shinigami" is referring to their ability to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami", {\alpha&HFF&}could mean that they'll confirm each other's identity by demonstrating their ability to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Confirm our identities by showing each other our Shinigami", could mean that they'll confirm each other's identity by demonstrating their ability to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we can consider "Shinigami" as a common term of some significance between Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to try to clarify that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, will we reply again to guide them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we probe too deeply, {\alpha&HFF&}they may realize that we know nothing, and that we aren't really Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we probe too deeply, they may realize that we know nothing, and that we aren't really Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}From now on, we'll leave it to Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. From now on, we'll leave it to Kira and the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that having received a reply from Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}the second Kira is now content about the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that having received a reply from Kira, the second Kira is now content about the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:12:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They believe that they've successfully appealed to Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they are using words that only they would know the significance of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll repeat this reply on the 6:00pm news on Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira will be watching to view the interaction between the second Kira and the fake Kira that we've created.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Kira would want to avoid any contact between the second Kira and the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky, {\alpha&HFF&}we'll get a response from the real Kira this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're lucky, we'll get a response from the real Kira this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if we don't receive a response from Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... {\alpha&HFF&}I've tried to think of what the second Kira would do in this situation, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I've tried to think of what the second Kira would do in this situation, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they would probably tell the police and the public further information that Kira would not want them to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to force Kira to seek an audience with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be very interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even more interesting if Kira does fear such a response, and sends their own message by video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that does happen, we'll have more physical evidence against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the time being, {\alpha&HFF&}let us pursue the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for the time being, let us pursue the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. That's so hot, Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired... {\alpha&HFF&}Being a model is all about having stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired... Being a model is all about having stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami need to have a Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Shinigami to play with humans, they need to have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami, Ryuk, who gave a notebook to Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}tricked the Shinigami Overlord and got a second notebook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami, Ryuk, who gave a notebook to Kira, tricked the Shinigami Overlord and got a second notebook, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. {\alpha&HFF&}The Shinigami Overlord isn't that easy to trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The Shinigami Overlord isn't that easy to trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how did you manage it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rare in the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the few who actually knows how to kill a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you killed a Shinigami, and gave Misa their notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}I didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be there when a Shinigami died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, {\alpha&HFF&}tell me how to kill a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell me how to kill a Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to kill a Shinigami is... {\alpha&HFF&}to make them fall in love with a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to kill a Shinigami is... to make them fall in love with a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful way to kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was once a Shinigami named Jealous, who used to constantly gaze at one particular girl from his place in the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the Shinigami world, Jealous was always, always watching that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's today, isn't it? {\alpha&HFF&}That girl's life runs out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's today, isn't it? That girl's life runs out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.59,0:15:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems so full of life... {\alpha&HFF&}I wonder why it's today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems so full of life... I wonder why it's today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... {\alpha&HFF&}why today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder... why today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also became curious as to how she would die, {\alpha&HFF&}so I chose to watch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also became curious as to how she would die, so I chose to watch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking alone late at night... {\alpha&HFF&}and then..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was walking alone late at night... and then..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly a man appeared from an alley, and confessed his love for the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you more than anyone in this world!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to watch over, and protect you forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl, having never seen the man before, {\alpha&HFF&}naturally refused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl, having never seen the man before, naturally refused him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... {\alpha&HFF&}I'll kill you... before killing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll kill you... {\alpha&HFF&}before killing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... I'll kill you... before killing myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {\alpha&HFF&}Stop that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous did something that no Shinigami should ever do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous used his Death Note to save that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami exist solely to take human lives in order to increase their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, {\alpha&HFF&}Jealous turned into sand, or rust... something I couldn't identify... and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Jealous turned into sand, or rust... something I couldn't identify... {\alpha&HFF&}and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Jealous turned into sand, or rust... something I couldn't identify... and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous's life was added to the lifespan of the girl he had been watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't in love with that girl, {\alpha&HFF&}he wouldn't have died?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wasn't in love with that girl, he wouldn't have died?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person... {\alpha&HFF&}who helped me back then... was Jealous, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person... who helped me back then... {\alpha&HFF&}was Jealous, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the person... who helped me back then... was Jealous, the Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous was in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why that notebook is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}You've got to make a Shinigami fall in love and help someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You've got to make a Shinigami fall in love and help someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Rem? {\alpha&HFF&}You aren't falling for me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you Rem? You aren't falling for me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up. {\alpha&HFF&}You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up. You can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, {\alpha&HFF&}so you guessed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you guessed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have something else I can tell Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they know {\alpha&HFF&}how to kill a Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they know how to kill a Shinigami?
